Student Financial Planning : Packaging

Created by Stephen Hutchinson, last modified by Angshuman Mukherjee on Mar 04, 2021

The Packaging Subject contains Student Packaging Information.

Views highlighted in RED are top level views.  The column names displayed in the diagram indicate columns used to join to other views. 

Subject Relationships

SUBJECTRELATIONSHIP
STUDENTENROLLMENT_ID
AWARDINGENROLLMENT_ID, FUND_CODE, ACADEMIC_YEAR_AWARD_YEAR
SAFIENROLLMENT_ID, SAFI_VERSION
